OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779390672
OL,3,CPupils evacuated during exam following
OL,4,Cbomb threat at school
OL,6,FPupils sitting a GCSE exam had to be
OL,7,Fevacuated from the classroom after the
OL,8,Fschool received a bomb threat.
OL,10,FStaff at Parklands High School in
OL,11,FChorley said an email was received on
OL,12,FWednesday 20 May while year 11
OL,13,Fstudents were sitting an exam.
OL,15,FThe school triggered the fire alarm,
OL,16,Fand pupils were sent home after the
OL,17,Fdecision was made to close for the day.
OL,19,FLancashire Police later confirmed the
OL,20,Fthreat was 'non-credible', with no
OL,21,Frisk to students or staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
