OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779390672
OL,3,CPupils evacuated during exam following
OL,4,Cbomb threat at school
OL,6,FIn a statement, a Parklands High
OL,7,FSchool spokesperson said: "We have
OL,8,Fdealt with a challenging situation at
OL,9,Fschool today. Please be assured that
OL,10,Fthroughout the incident, our absolute
OL,11,Fpriority was the safety and well-being
OL,12,Fof our children.
OL,14,F"You may have seen reports in the
OL,15,Fmedia regarding a bomb threat email
OL,16,Freceived by the school. In line with
OL,17,Four safety procedures, we initiated an
OL,18,Fimmediate evacuation and contacted
OL,19,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779390672
OL,3,CPupils evacuated during exam following
OL,4,Cbomb threat at school
OL,6,F"The police attended the scene,
OL,7,Fthoroughly assessed the situation, and
OL,8,Fhave formally assured us that this was
OL,9,Fa non-credible threat and there was no
OL,10,Frisk to pupils and staff. The school
OL,11,Fbuilding has since been fully secured
OL,12,Ffor the night."
OL,14,FThe school spokesperson said a full
OL,15,Freport will be sent to the exam board
OL,16,Ffor consideration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
