PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779390672
OL,3,CPupils evacuated during exam following
OL,4,Cbomb threat at school
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Lancashire Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "At 10.23am we received a report
OL,8,Fthat Parklands High School had been
OL,9,Fsubject to a bomb threat and has been
OL,10,Fevacuated. This was a decision made by
OL,11,Fthe school.
OL,13,F"While at this time we do not believe
OL,14,Fthis to be a genuine threat and there
OL,15,Fis no risk towards any of the
OL,16,Fstudents, staff or members of the
OL,17,Fpublic, officers have attended as
OL,18,Freassurance.
OL,20,F"We are investigating and anyone with
OL,21,Finformation should call 101."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
